*.pyc

# packaging build artifacts (2026-07-18, pyproject.toml added) - `python
# -m build` and `pip install -e .` both write these; neither is source.
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# `dafny run`/`dafny build` compiler byproducts (C# target, the default
# here) - not source, not captured evidence. Added 2026-07-15 building
# the R5 differential-testing harness, whose driver .dfy is run
# directly rather than just verified, unlike every other .dfy in this
# repo (see run_verify_dafny.py's own `dafny verify`-only convention).
obj/
*.dll
*.pdb
*.deps.json
*.runtimeconfig.json
examples/*/dosage_differential_driver
examples/*/dosage_differential_driver.cs
examples/*/dosage_differential_driver.csproj
